Package: chartjs
Title: Interactive Charts for R Using Chart.js
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chart.js R", "Maintainer", , "maintainer@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Create interactive charts in R using the Chart.js JavaScript library. 
    Supports all Chart.js chart types including bar, line, scatter, bubble, pie, 
    doughnut, radar, and polar area charts with full animation and plugin support. 
    Integrates seamlessly with Shiny applications.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
