    htmlwidgets (>= 1.5.4),
    htmltools,
    jsonlite,
    magrittr
Suggests:
    shiny,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/ashgreat/chartjs
BugReports: https://github.com/ashgreat/chartjs/issues
